content: Wrote an article for the sustainable tech magazine. Highlighted our startup's commitment to ethical AI and sustainable financial solutions.
Investors are now looking at our documentation. They've asked for a meeting with our blockchain expert to discuss security protocols.
Had an insightful chat with my co-founder. We're realigning our focus on sustainability and how it ties into our tech. A new direction for us.
Just received confirmation for our next investor meeting. They're interested in our AI-driven sustainability initiatives. This is progress.
